{"tid":1105253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全港最抵食壽司專門店！","createTime":"2019-04-13T17:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T07:02:30.000Z","uid":199504,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d878882ede5996c1221b2fb6ac27e1b38181b7b3","tid":1105253,"uid":199504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:55:40.000Z","msg":"今日我突然想去食壽司<br />\n行過一間壽司鋪 見佢幾多人排 就諗住試試佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入到去個侍應話咩用手機點餐 我心諗 嘩 咩而家食個壽司都咁先進架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當我食飽飽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗住買單嗰陣 見到張單<br />\n<br />\n嘩 乜原來咁抵食架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gCkcc60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgCkcc60.png&h=b3b40923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我就擺低張單 頭也不回咁走左<br />\n<br />\n我而家後悔無叫多幾件做宵夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a691862d1762fc802c0e9e1918c3f0025cb61bbc","tid":1105253,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:57:22.000Z","msg":"乞衣仔"},{"pid":"650b5513c4229a65a4144c2bf49cfdbb22600727","tid":1105253,"uid":77985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T18:07:40.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打咁大篇野無人會信囉"},{"pid":"89ea6cc4691ac4fa1912ef09ecd69172d3c66c82","tid":1105253,"uid":30708,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1